<div class="section" id="columns">
  <div class="container">
    <details class="details">
      <summary>
        <h1>Columns</h1>
        <p>Listed are the various default stylings and sub-categories of typographic helpers.</p>
      </summary>
      <div class="box is-big has-shadow">
        <p class="label">Default, columns are aligned to the left; <code class="code">&lt;div class="<strong>columns</strong> <em>{horizontal-modifiers} {vertical-modifiers}</em>"&gt;</code></p>
        <div class="columns box is-grouped has-background-light">
          <div class="column box">Col A</div>
          <div class="column box">Col B</div>
          <div class="column box">Col C</div>
        </div>
        <p class="label">Even distribution with gap and edge spacing equally divided; <code class="code">&lt;div class="columns <strong>is-even</strong>"&gt;</code></p>
        <div class="columns box is-even has-background-light">
          <div class="column box">Col A</div>
          <div class="column box">Col B</div>
          <div class="column box">Col C</div>
        </div>
        <p class="label">Even distribution in the line from start to end; <code class="code">&lt;div class="columns <strong>is-between</strong>"&gt;</code></p>
        <div class="columns box is-between has-background-light">
          <div class="column box">Col A</div>
          <div class="column box">Col B</div>
          <div class="column box">Col C</div>
        </div>
        <p class="label">Even distribution in the line with equal space; <code class="code">&lt;div class="columns <strong>is-around</strong>"&gt;</code></p>
        <div class="columns is-around box has-background-light">
          <div class="column box">Col A</div>
          <div class="column box">Col B</div>
          <div class="column box">Col C</div>
        </div>
        <p class="label">Columns aligned to the left; <code class="code">&lt;div class="columns <strong>is-left</strong>"&gt;</code></p>
        <div class="columns is-left box has-background-light">
          <div class="column box">Col A</div>
          <div class="column box">Col B</div>
          <div class="column box">Col C</div>
        </div>
        <p class="label">Columns aligned to the right; <code class="code">&lt;div class="columns <strong>is-right</strong>"&gt;</code></p>
        <div class="columns is-right box has-background-light">
          <div class="column box">Col A</div>
          <div class="column box">Col B</div>
          <div class="column box">Col C</div>
        </div>
        <p class="label">Columns aligned to the center; <code class="code">&lt;div class="columns <strong>is-center</strong>"&gt;</code></p>
        <div class="columns is-center box has-background-light">
          <div class="column box">Col A</div>
          <div class="column box">Col B</div>
          <div class="column box">Col C</div>
        </div>
        <p class="label">Maximum width consumption for columns; <code class="code">&lt;div class="columns <strong>is-divided</strong>"&gt;</code></p>
        <div class="columns is-divided box has-background-light">
          <div class="column box">Col A</div>
          <div class="column box">Col B</div>
          <div class="column box">Col C</div>
        </div>
        <p class="label">Vertical alignment of columns in the middle; <code class="code">&lt;div class="columns <strong>is-vcenter</strong>"&gt;</code></p>
        <div class="columns is-vcenter box has-background-light">
          <div class="column box">Col A</div>
          <div class="column box">Col B<br />Col B</div>
          <div class="column box">Col C</div>
        </div>
        <p class="label">Vertical alignment of columns on the bottom; <code class="code">&lt;div class="columns <strong>is-vbottom</strong>"&gt;</code></p>
        <div class="columns is-vbottom box has-background-light">
          <div class="column box">Col A</div>
          <div class="column box">Col B<br />Col B</div>
          <div class="column box">Col C</div>
        </div>
        <p class="label">'Stretch' column heights so all the columns have an equal height; <code class="code">&lt;div class="columns <strong>is-vstretch</strong>"&gt;</code></p>
        <div class="columns is-vstretch box has-background-light">
          <div class="column box">Col A</div>
          <div class="column box">Col B<br />Col B</div>
          <div class="column box">Col C</div>
        </div>
        <p class="label">Force columns to render vertically; <code class="code">&lt;div class="columns <strong>is-vertical</strong>"&gt;</code></p>
        <div class="columns is-vertical box has-background-light">
          <div class="column box">Col A</div>
          <div class="column box">Col B</div>
          <div class="column box">Col C</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </details>
  </div>
